ActOther Than Statutory Authority
SubjectCanada-Israel - Protocol Amending the Free Trade Agreement (CIFTA)
PrecisOrder Authorizing the Prime Minister or the Minister of Foreign Affairs to Sign, or the Minister of Foreign to delegate authority to sign, on behalf of the Government of Canada, the AGREEMENT to amend, in respect of the FREE TRADE AGREEMENT between the Government of Canada and the GOVERNMENT OF THE STATE OF ISRAEL that entered into force in 1997.
